RECELLED_I18N_CONTRIBUTE: Want to help translate ReCelled? Go to our [Weblate]({weblateUrl})!
RECELLED_SETTINGS_ADVANCED_DESC: Don't touch stuff in here if you don't know what you're doing. Unexpected things can happen to your cat.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_BACKEND_DESC: URL used to fetch some assets and to query ReCelled's REST API.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_DISCORD_EXPERIMENTS_DE: ****WARNING:**** Enabling this gives you access to features that can be detected by Discord and may result in an ****account termination****. ReCelled is **not responsible** for what you do with this feature. Leave it disabled if you are unsure. The ReCelled Team will **not** provide any support regarding any experiment. **Requires restart**.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_KEEP_TOKEN_DESC: Prevents Discord from removing your token from localStorage, reducing the number of unwanted logouts.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_OVERLAY_DESC: Opens a DevTools window that lets you inspect what's happening within Discord's in-game overlay.
RECELLED_SNIPPET_LINE1: Snippet from #css-snippets applied the {date, date, medium} at {date, time, medium}
RECELLED_UPDATES_AVAILABLE: {count, plural, =1 {# update is} other {# updates are}} available.
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_AUTO_DESC: ReCelled will automatically check for updates and show you an alert when one is available. Updates will not be installed until you choose to update it. Only official addons will be checked automatically.
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_DEBUG_DESC: Things that you may find useful for troubleshooting or flexing on some stats.
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_INTERVAL_DESC: How frequently ReCelled will check for updates. Minimum 10 minutes.
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_RELEASE_MODAL: Are you sure you want to change your release channel? ReCelled will reload your Discord client.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_NO_CLYDE_DESC: Replaces [Clyde]({clydeUrl}) in ReCelled commands with a mixed range of avatars and usernames selected by plug-in developers - fallbacks to "ReCelled" by default.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_RESTART: This setting requires you to restart Discord to take effect. Do you want to restart Discord now?
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_CHANGE_LOGS_DESC: Missed the change log, or want to see it again?
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_CONCURRENCY_DESC: How many concurrent tasks ReCelled will run in the background to check for updates. Minimum 1. If unsure, leave 2.
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_RELEASE_DESC: You can choose between the stable branch, or the development branch. Stable branch will only get major updates, security and critical updates. If unsure, stay on stable.
RECELLED_UPDATES_OPTS_TOAST_ENABLED_DESC: Show an overlay over the client which says updates are being checked for, and if updates are found, prompt you to update. Only applies if update in background is disabled.
RECELLED_PLUGIN_EMBED_WHATISTHIS_CONTENT:
This is a ReCelled feature. It allows you to install plugins or themes straight from chat.
Simply hit the install button on the embed.
RECELLED_ERROR_AN_ERROR_OCCURRED_COMMAND: An error occurred while executing the command:
RECELLED_ERROR_CHECK_CONSOLE: Check the console for more details.
RECELLED_NOTICES_WELCOME_NEW_USER: Welcome! ReCelled has been successfully injected into your Discord client. Feel free to join our Discord server for announcements, support and more!
RECELLED_SETTINGS_ERROR_HEADER: Something went wrong rendering this element!
RECELLED_SETTINGS_ERROR_RENDER_PANEL: An error occurred while rendering settings panel.
RECELLED_ADDON_UNINSTALL_PROMPT_BODY: Are you sure you want to uninstall this {type}? This cannot be undone.
RECELLED_TOAST_INSTALLER_ADDON_LOAD_FAIL: {name} was installed but could not be loaded.
RECELLED_TOAST_INSTALLER_ADDON_FETCH_INF: Failed to get info for addon.
RECELLED_ADDON_AUTHORS_MANY: by {author1}, {author2}, {author3}, and {count, plural, =1 {# other} other {# others}}
RECELLED_UPDATES_TOAST_NEW: {count, plural, =1 {# new update} other {# new updates}} available!
RECELLED_PLUGIN_INSTALL_RELOAD_PROMPT_BO: {name} requires a reload to work properly. Reload now?
RECELLED_SETTINGS_BADGES_DESC: Show custom ReCelled badges on user profiles.
RECELLED_DEVELOPER_MODE_WARNING: You are currently running ReCelled in developer mode and ReCelled will not be able to update itself. [Switch to production mode]({url}).
RECELLED_ADDON_NOT_REVIEWED_DESC: This {type} has not been reviewed by the ReCelled team and could harm your computer. Use at your own risk.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_QUICKCSS_AUTO_APPLY_DE: Automatically apply changes to Quick CSS as you type.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_DEV_COMPANION_DESC: Reconnects the Dev Companion coremod to the VSCode extension.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_REACT_DEVTOOLS_DESC: Loads the React DevTools extension, allowing you to inspect the React tree and debug more easily. **Requires restart**.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_ADDON_EMBEDS_DESC: Show a card with information on an addon when a store/install link is shared in chat.
RECELLED_COMMAND_ERROR_GENERIC: Something went wrong, please try again later. If this issue persists, please contact the ReCelled team.
RECELLED_COMMAND_LIST_ERROR_SPECIFY: You need to specify whether to send a plugin or theme list
RECELLED_SETTINGS_TRANSPARENT_ISSUES_WIN: ****WARNING:**** This is break **window snapping**. In some cases, you make experience a black background, such as when the window is cut off at the top or bottom due to the monitor resolution, or when the development tools are open and docked.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_TRANSPARENT_ISSUES_LIN: ****WARNING:**** Hardware acceleration** may need to be turned **off**. In some cases, you may experience a black background, such as when the window is cut off at the top of bottom due to the monitor resolution, or when the development tools are opened and docked.
RECELLED_SETTINGS_TRANSPARENT_DESC: Makes the Discord window transparent, primarily useful for theming. **Requires restart**.
RECELLED_COMMAND_LIST_OPTION_SEND_DESC: Share the list publicly in chat
RECELLED_COMMAND_LIST_OPTION_TYPE_DESC: What type of addons to show
RECELLED_COMMAND_LIST_OPTION_VERSION_DES: Include version numbers in the list
RECELLED_COMMAND_LIST_OPTION_STATUS_DESC: Whether to show addons that are enabled, disabled or both
RECELLED_COMMAND_INSTALL_OPTION_ADDON_DE: Identifier of the addon to install from the source
RECELLED_COMMAND_INSTALL_OPTION_SOURCE_D: Source to install the addon from
RECELLED_COMMAND_INSTALL_OPTION_ID_DESC: If the source has multiple addons, specify which one to install
